			<div class="container-fluid">
				<div class="row cb-slideshow-text-container ">
					<div class= "tm-content d-flex flex-column  justify-content-center col-xl-6 col-sm-8 col-xs-8 section blocks">
						<header class="mb-5"><h1> Go Panda's</h1></header>
						<p class="mb-3 text-white h2">Decentralised, Secure & Free Conferencing</p>
						<p class="mb-5 text-light text-justify">Panda's is a new type of conferencing web app. 
							You choose where your messages are stored,
